crystal-stacker: crystal-stacker (Match 3 or more of the same color crystals blocks)
crystal-stacker:
crystal-stacker: If you've played Columns then you know what Crystal Stacker is all
crystal-stacker: about. Match 3 or more of the same color crystals either horizontally,
crystal-stacker: vertically, or diagonally to destroy them. For every 45 crystals you
crystal-stacker: destroy, the level increases and the crystals fall faster. The higher
crystal-stacker: the level, the more points you are awarded for destroying crystals.
crystal-stacker:
crystal-stacker: http://www.t3-i.com/cstacker.htm
